                        {
                            "type": "paragraph",
                            "content": [
                                {
                                    "text": "We care about being right and it often takes reasoning from first principles to get there.",
                                    "style": []
                                }
                            ]
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "heading_3",
                            "text": "Global optimization"
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "paragraph",
                            "content": [
                                {
                                    "text": "We do what\u2019s best for the organization overall.",
