        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": [
                {
                    "text": "To make this possible, we\u2019ve brought together a diverse team of individuals passionate about computing, history, art, alternative programming languages, music, skateboarding, and craft. Today, we\u2019re growing faster than ever across offices in San Francisco, New York, Dublin, Hyderabad and Tokyo\u00a0\ud83c\uddfa\ud83c\uddf8\u00a0\ud83c\uddee\ud83c\uddea\u00a0\ud83c\uddee\ud83c\uddf3\u00a0\ud83c\uddef\ud83c\uddf5",
