{
    "type": "page",
    "title": "Annual performance self-review",
    "icon": "\ud83d\uddfa\ufe0f",
    "children": [
        {
            "type": "heading_1",
            "text": "Step 1: Identify the Year's Yay Moments"
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": [
                {
                    "text": "A whole year is hard to get through (especially this year). ",
                    "style": [
                        "bold"
                    ]
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": [
                {
                    "text": "But look at you! You did it! \ud83c\udf89 ",
                    "style": [
                        "bold"
                    ]
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": [
                {
                    "text": "You made progress this year, even if it doesn't always feel like it. ",
                    "style": [
                        "bold"
                    ]
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": [
                {
                    "text": "Think of all the projects finished. The problems solved. The laughs and smiles made.",
                    "style": []
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": [
                {
                    "text": "Don't leave them behind, forgotten, in this calendar year.",
                    "style": []
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": [
                {
                    "text": "Name them. Celebrate them. Let them give you confidence you can handle what next year brings. \ud83d\ude4c",
                    "style": []
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "heading_3",
            "text": "Add your year's yay moments\u2014no matter how big or small they feel\u2014here:"
        },
        {
            "type": "bulleted_list",
            "items": [
                "Start here\u2026"
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "heading_3",
            "text": "Now, think: what can you do to lean into these existing wins further next year?"
        },
        {
            "type": "bulleted_list",
            "items": [
                "Start here\u2026"
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": []
        },
        {
            "type": "heading_1",
            "text": "Step 2: Recognize the Rough Spots"
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": [
                {
                    "text": "Like we established before, making it through the year isn't easy. It's a given not everything went as planned. ",
                    "style": []
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": [
                {
                    "text": "And focusing on your wins doesn't mean you need to be in denial about your losses...no room for toxic positivity around here!",
                    "style": []
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
