                    "type": "toggle",
                    "title": "Labs",
                    "children": [
                        {
                            "type": "paragraph",
                            "content": [
                                {
                                    "text": "Labs are designed to provide practical experience and reinforce the concepts taught in lectures. Each lab will focus on a specific topic, and students will be expected to complete coding tasks during the lab session. Lab attendance is crucial as it counts towards your final grade.",
                                    "style": []
                                }
                            ]
                        }
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "type": "toggle",
                    "title": "Assignments",
                    "children": [
                        {
                            "type": "paragraph",
                            "content": [
                                {
                                    "text": "Assignments are designed to test your understanding of the course material. They will consist of coding problems that you will need to solve individually. Assignments will be more complex than lab tasks and will often require you to apply concepts from multiple lectures.",
                                    "style": []
                                }
                            ]
                        }
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "type": "toggle",
                    "title": "Midterm and Final Exam",
                    "children": [
                        {
                            "type": "paragraph",
                            "content": [
                                {
                                    "text": "The midterm will cover all material taught up to that point in the course. The final exam will cover all course material. Both exams will consist of multiple-choice questions, short answer questions, and coding problems. Studying lecture notes and assignments is the best way to prepare.",
                                    "style": []
                                }
                            ]
                        }
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "type": "toggle",
                    "title": "Participation",
                    "children": [
                        {
                            "type": "paragraph",
                            "content": [
                                {
                                    "text": "Participation marks are awarded based on your engagement in the course. This includes posting and responding to questions on the discussion board, attending tutorials, and participating in class discussions. Regular engagement is crucial for doing well in this part of the assessment.",
                                    "style": []
                                }
                            ]
                        }
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "type": "heading_2",
                    "text": "Penalties for lateness"
